{"tid":1492094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[非專業(2)] [徇眾要求] 我想用我嘅統計學幫下民陣","createTime":"2019-08-20T16:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T14:11:41.000Z","uid":70201,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5e57ac3c874369a6a25c5c5b32777a5ee4334532","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">前言：<br />\n6月9日 百萬大遊行 警方話高峰時得廿四萬人參與遊行<br />\n我條氣唔順 於是決定自己試下統計人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>[非專業] 我想知我統計學有冇警察咁差<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1199754\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1199754</a></blockquote><br />\n然後ILoveU3000巴打就提出咗毅進制呢個概念 再由愛情波函數巴打將其發揚光大<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zBGhhR7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzBGhhR7.png&h=72daafea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將我推算嘅數字應用落毅進制度 結果都幾接近！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span> <br />\n<br />\n好！入正題！<br />\n民陣宣布喺銅鑼灣、天后及維園一帶，有 170 萬人參與 8.18「流水式集會」。呢個數字當然鼓舞，但係好多人都覺得，實際人數唔止咁少！<br />\n事實上，民陣都指出「行動規模與 6.16 相若，但由於警方不合理限制，令大會未能點算灣仔、金鐘一帶未能進入維園的市民人數，相信今日 (8.18) 為相同訴求上街的市民，<strong>遠超 170 萬</strong>。」。<br />\n有巴絲覺得唔忿氣，叫我再出多個post統計 8.18 嘅活動人數<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">多謝咁多位仲記得小妹個post</span>，所以我就決定幫民陣計哂由炮台山去到金鐘，全日有幾多人為咗香港行出嚟！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">再利申：我只係睇住港大民意研究計劃個方法，盡量有樣學樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n根據港大民意研究計劃，警方喺往年七一大遊行，採用每平方米二點三六人，作為計算遊行人數嘅基準；綜合報章文字報道，以遊行龍頭抵達終審法院、龍尾為炮台山站近康福臺作推算，成個「流水式集會」總共<strong>佔地超過三十一萬平方米</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n考慮到八一八當日集會期間，人口密度會比遊行高；同時因天氣不穩，市民不時需要舉起雨傘，令人口密度稍為下降，因此以遊行隊伍<strong>每平方米二點三人</strong>作基準，遊行路面<strong>單一時間能夠容納超過七十萬人</strong>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcQqGuK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcQqGuK.png&h=3890e123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重要事項：<br />\n1. 因為實在無法記錄所有市民途經的道路及佔用的時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，因此只會在此記錄<strong>由炮台山地鐵站對出英皇道，途經維園對出幾條橫街、軒尼詩道、告士打道，抵達遮打花園對出遮打道的路線。</strong><br />\n2. 同時，由於「流水式集會」，維園內的人流難以統計，因此亦<strong>假定維園內的市民一直保持移動。多出的人數誤差，將用作填補上述因忽略統計其他街道，所造成的誤差</strong>。</span><br />\n<br />\n參考隊頭用約兩小時十分鐘由維園到達終審法院，全程大約四公里。「流水式集會」於約三時開始，隊尾約十時抵達金鐘。如果以七小時為基準，假設<strong>每程需時平均二點五小時</strong>。換言之，唔包括中途加入以及提前離開嘅人士，<strong>總共有二點八程</strong>出發。<br />\n<br />\n由此得出，最後推算遊行人數為 2.8 x 760063 = <strong>2128176人</strong>。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AF61Zgv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAF61Zgv.png&h=070681f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方：維園內同一時間最高峰出席人數為十二萬八千人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"d332364adda67995bb02ceeb170ba4a595994340","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:23:22.000Z","msg":"同場加映：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R7t7UTx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR7t7UTx.png&h=bd676bc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XC65GvC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXC65GvC.png&h=c6d2833a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n留意返 呢個係假設佢地每平方米企四個 逼過逼地鐵咁撐警 實際係點大家有眼睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBQRB5Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBQRB5Y.jpg&h=a94ea0a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2514f083292b2386af4ac7303022eb6ccafb4b8e","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:24:02.000Z","msg":"地圖參考：<br />\nshorturl.at/anACN<br />\nshorturl.at/cimyC<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源：<br />\nshorturl.at/iDHK0<br />\nshorturl.at/gnKO9<br />\nshorturl.at/nqxPW"},{"pid":"812bb04e218e43ca9c0965568caebd3685e418dd","tid":1492094,"uid":175159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FRaqHpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFRaqHpr.jpg&h=9af3359d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AMMxnpr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAMMxnpr.jpg&h=487c37d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7b3PpCM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7b3PpCM.jpg&h=4dcd610f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VzCyv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VzCyv6.jpg&h=8198a13a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2405f816add6e589a5329696b48f0a6e71a39302","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"768825480855c1a3508cd761e8c1c03b459dccc5","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b25acbd398a8b05e526cd5ed54674fd485f9e956","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:25:59.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"5fdf26dff650a84ff3e197f7746906c95ef65715","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:26:10.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"39d7479f8d54190f332198e334df0c4792beba11","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"1635bcf65efdf4568fb0129e4375e273bb139873","tid":1492094,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T16:26:32.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"eca33fc0a716b3d12e3d6e38df1d8f3f9205d2b1","tid":1492094,"uid":7020